<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.8.11">
<l>uyiriṉāṟ kuṟaivillā vulakēḻtaṉ ṉuḷḷoṭukki</l>
<l>tayirveṇṇe yuṇṭāṉait taṭaṅkurukūrc caṭakōpaṉ</l>
<l>ceyirilcol licaimālai yāyirattu ḷippattāl</l>
<l>vayirañcēr piṟappaṟuttu vaikunta naṇṇuvarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>By these ten among the thousand in the musical garland composed without fault</l>
<l>by Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr with a tank on him who ate curd [and] ghee,</l>
<l>restraining in his self all the seven worlds which are without lack of lives</l>
<l>they will approach Vaikunta, cutting off birth, joined by harshness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
